Subject: [PATCH 4.19 191/293] video: fbdev: kyro: Error out if pixclock equals zero
Date:   Mon, 20 Sep 2021 18:42:33 +0200
Message-Id: <20210920163939.807428218@linuxfoundation.org>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.33.0
